<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM10.9">
<l>kaṭalē kaṭalē uṉṉaik kaṭaintu kalakkuṟuttu</l>
<l>uṭaluḷ pukuntuniṉ ṟūṟa laṟuttavaṟ keṉṉaiyu</l>
<l>muṭaluḷ pukuntuniṉ ṟūṟa laṟukkiṉṟa māyaṟkeṉ</l>
<l>naṭalaika ḷellām nākaṇaik kēceṉṟu raittiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O ocean! O ocean! Will you go to the serpent-bed itself and tell of all my sufferings</l>
<l>to the [Lord] who churned you, caused [you] to be agitated,</l>
<l>and harvested the essence by entering and remaining in [your] body;</l>
<l>to the Deceitful [Lord] who harvests [my] essence by also entering my body?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
